    </pre>
    <h2>Appendix B: Complete Folder Hierarchy</h2>
    <pre>
PathVision_Final/
├── main.py                     # Main execution runtime orchestrator
├── config.py                   # Centralized configuration structures
├── perception/
│   ├── pathvision_trt.py       # PathVision Segmentation TensorRT wrapper
│   ├── depth_trt.py           # Depth Anything V2 TensorRT wrapper
│   └── scene_fusion.py         # Multi-model spatial fusion engine
├── navigation/
│   ├── path_geometry.py       # Geometric analyzer for walkable paths
│   ├── safety.py               # Safety state evaluator
│   └── decision.py             # Direction command generator
├── reasoning/
│   ├── situation_manager.py    # Situation and Interaction mode classifier
│   ├── conversation_memory.py   # Speech deduplication and reassurance controller
│   ├── prompts.py              # LLM prompt builder and offline fallback logic
│   └── scene_memory.py         # Historical scene data ring buffer
└── speech/
    └── kokoro.py               # Preemptive priority Kokoro TTS speaker
    </pre>
