    <pre>
[Camera Ingest Thread] ──(Shared Frame)──> [Inference Loop Thread]
                                                   │
[Qwen Query Thread]   <──(Scene Payload)───────┘
                                                   │
[Telemetry Thread]     <──(Logs / Images)────────┘
    </pre>
    <h2>Appendix F: Glossary of Terms</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>TensorRT:</strong> High-performance deep learning inference library from NVIDIA.</li>
        <li><strong>Softmax:</strong> Converts output logits into normalized probability scores.</li>
        <li><strong>FPS:</strong> Frames Per Second, measuring execution frequency.</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Appendix G: Abbreviations</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>LLM:</strong> Large Language Model</li>
        <li><strong>TTS:</strong> Text-To-Speech</li>
        <li><strong>TRT:</strong> TensorRT</li>
        <li><strong>GPU:</strong> Graphics Processing Unit</li>
    </ul>

